problems: ?


to run this app:
1- open a nodejs command prompt window
    cd /Applications/XAMPP/htdocs/mycraigfp99
    node server.js
    // a server will start running

2- make sure the mysql server is running on Macbook air:
    click on xamp-control.exe
    start mysql (dont need to start Apache server since we already have Nodejs server running

3- on a web browser, type  localhost:3000


